---
Run the deterministic dream cycle: promote top cluster to LESSONS.md, prune decayed episodic events

Usage: dream [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --dry
          Dry run: print what would change without writing. Not yet implemented; ships v0.1.1

      --no-commit
          Skip the autobiography commit. The cycle still runs and writes to disk; only the git2 commit step is skipped. Useful in CI

  -h, --help
          Print help
